{"tid":164294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國街頭宛如影集「陰屍路」！　全因新毒品Spice導致","createTime":"2017-03-20T14:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T14:38:52.000Z","uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f18e95fd032438a1af5c432fac3344ee1b873270","tid":164294,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"英國街頭宛如影集「陰屍路」！　全因新毒品Spice導致<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=232773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D232773&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f89e1e9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D232773&h=41cae9e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=232773</a><br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n英國街頭近日出現宛如美劇「陰屍路」場景，據英國《每日郵報》報導，英國曼徹斯特街頭隨處可見兩眼無神，走路有如行屍一般的人，全因中國大陸及印度大量製造的新品種毒品「Spice」造成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/nintchdbpict0003100427731.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=960&amp;quality=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fnintchdbpict0003100427731.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26w%3D960%26quality%3D100&h=12d96641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/03/12/838461-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2F838461-XXL.jpg&h=f8987724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲英國街頭出現影集「陰屍路」場景（圖／翻攝自每日郵報）<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，新品種毒品「Spice」，最初被英國視為「合法」大麻替代品在當地公開販售，直到去年發生多起死亡事故，當局才意識到危險，在去（2016）年5月立法禁止販售，但為時已晚，無法阻止毒品在市面流竄。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，Spice會導致心跳加速、嘔吐、癲癇發作、精神異常等症狀，效果是大麻的100倍，加上Spice價格低廉，在曼徹斯特1公克僅需3英鎊（約台幣120元），且起先是「合法」販售，導致現今街頭隨處可以買到。英國慈善團體（Lifeshare）估計有95%曼徹斯特遊民都吸食過Spice。"},{"pid":"431a8ddba9311108625b508550a3f88890f6259a","tid":164294,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/marvelcinematicuniverse/images/e/ec/Steel_Serpent_2.PNG/revision/latest?cb=20150422050539\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fmarvelcinematicuniverse%2Fimages%2Fe%2Fec%2FSteel_Serpent_2.PNG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20150422050539&h=0372745a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15c3da9ed42843884a33669448610f8716070bc9","tid":164294,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.idigitaltimes.com/sites/idigitaltimes.com/files/styles/image_embed/public/2017/02/09/steel-serpent.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.idigitaltimes.com%2Fsites%2Fidigitaltimes.com%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fimage_embed%2Fpublic%2F2017%2F02%2F09%2Fsteel-serpent.jpg&h=cdff3fb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28d364addca172f5fba78582ddfd0ad343fb2e62","tid":164294,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}